{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-about-page-js","path":"/about/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>I'm Microsoft Teams and Skype for Business specialist who also likes to learn <code>$newThings</code> in the meantime.</p>\n<p>Current values of <code>$newThings</code> for me is <code>[JavaScript, Web Development, CSS]</code>. It might be subject to change frequently.</p>\n<h3 id=\"blog\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#blog\" aria-label=\"blog permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Blog</h3>\n<p>On this blog I include some random hints/instructions about the issues I have resolved and decided to note so I don't have to search for the information once again. I'm glad if you find it somewhat useful!</p>\n<h3 id=\"credits\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#credits\" aria-label=\"credits permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Credits</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Built  by <a href=\"https://netlify.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Netlify</a> on <a href=\"https://gatsbyjs.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Gatsby</a></li>\n<li>Hosted on <a href=\"https://pages.github.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GitHub pages</a></li>\n<li>Cover photo by <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@cdr6934?utm_source=unsplash&#x26;utm_medium=referral&#x26;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Chris Ried</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/s/photos/tech?utm_source=unsplash&#x26;utm_medium=referral&#x26;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Unsplash</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"About me"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"0da4a3d6-cf7c-50f8-98c5-3940c13ea5e8"}}}